{"tid":734820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高凶浩劫】The Rock大戰關禮傑？　狄維莊遜謙認：佢勁啲","createTime":"2018-07-09T03:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:49:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":447,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8e8ef9914dc4d2db34a1fac249d9e81270d858","tid":734820,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1624419/org/71fff141dc7dfaf31c2bfe6870f57d5c.jpg/IglRxO65ksBSGYPTVEriYYbxqPm_LCGQkkQb1ZJEG9U?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1624419%2Forg%2F71fff141dc7dfaf31c2bfe6870f57d5c.jpg%2FIglRxO65ksBSGYPTVEriYYbxqPm_LCGQkkQb1ZJEG9U%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=6273d6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狄維莊遜（Dwayne Johnson）今次在《高凶浩劫》（Skycraper）飾演的「韋索亞」跟以往有少少不同，前身是FBI救人隊隊長的他，在任務中被炸斷一條腳，靠義肢來繼續生活，雖然人生跌進谷底，卻讓韋索亞認識了太太（Neve Campbell飾），仲誕下一對可愛的龍鳳胎。後來韋索亞轉行做保安，為座落香港西九龍的全球最高大廈「明珠塔」負責保安工作。<br />\n<br />\n電影其中一幕重頭戲，講述明珠塔被恐怖分子放火，韋索亞家人身陷火海之中，生命危在旦夕，而身在大廈外的韋索亞，又因警方封鎖現場而無法進入大廈，為了拯救心愛的家人，他決定由大廈旁邊的起重機跳入明珠塔，需知道起跳點到落腳點的距離，是超越平凡人可誇過的極限，但對於不平凡的狄維莊遜來說，就可驚險地完成這個不可能的動作。<br />\n<br />\n不過大部分香港觀眾看到這一幕時，都不禁想起4年前播映的TVB劇集《叛逃》中，飾演反恐特警隊主管的關禮傑示範「世界級跳樓」，與《高凶浩劫》這一幕跳樓重頭戲相似度極高。小編向狄維莊遜及導演羅遜馬素費巴（Rawson Marshall Thurber）展示這片段，二人大感驚訝，不約而同大讚這一幕好正，而狄維莊遜仲連講3次：「應該這一場（關禮傑）比較好」，相當謙虛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1624450/org/816e085721360edae28caa72765ae7ea.jpg/PJWlsO-JUKoZ3ztGx9t00mvPYsIge64pT8GafE_Bmnw?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1624450%2Forg%2F816e085721360edae28caa72765ae7ea.jpg%2FPJWlsO-JUKoZ3ztGx9t00mvPYsIge64pT8GafE_Bmnw%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=ccedbf84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後小編再出示《高凶浩劫》海報，與謝天華在劇集《神槍狙撃》中「單手攀岩兼講電話」一幕的對比圖，狄維莊遜與羅遜馬素費巴的反應更加大，前者仲笑住話對方「你抄人」，而羅遜就一副慘慘豬樣回應：「你知原創橋真的好難度」，之後狄維莊遜仲踩多腳話下次要同《神槍狙撃》的導演合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/208202/%E9%AB%98%E5%87%B6%E6%B5%A9%E5%8A%AB-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-the-rock%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A6%AE%E5%82%91-%E7%8B%84%E7%B6%AD%E8%8E%8A%E9%81%9C%E8%AC%99%E8%AA%8D-%E4%BD%A2%E5%8B%81%E5%95%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F208202%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2587%25B6%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E5%258A%25AB-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-the-rock%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%2582%2591-%25E7%258B%2584%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%258E%258A%25E9%2581%259C%25E8%25AC%2599%25E8%25AA%258D-%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E5%258B%2581%25E5%2595%25B2&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=54f86e87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/208202/%E9%AB%98%E5%87%B6%E6%B5%A9%E5%8A%AB-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-the-rock%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A6%AE%E5%82%91-%E7%8B%84%E7%B6%AD%E8%8E%8A%E9%81%9C%E8%AC%99%E8%AA%8D-%E4%BD%A2%E5%8B%81%E5%95%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b665d660127efbf22eb4b42032f59c9ad8d21751","tid":734820,"uid":13653,"like":289,"dislike":4,"score":285,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"拎D膠劇同人比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3c03b02bf81c91f3b14019dd70ad04bd5f9ed8","tid":734820,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810dd5450b208af5e1b1e47d45cacd9e680f0ef1","tid":734820,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f215fea0a8966d7a1ef1d5d571c27c39bb17ac","tid":734820,"uid":15538,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201